ParallelChunk.en:
Two types of practice would be possible: either each country in question would be assessed in advance and a decision taken for that individual country on what proportion of the EIB's risk in the country was political in origin; 
          or
         each financing decision should have an assessment annexed to it concerning the division of the risk between political and economic factors.

